title: The Recruit - S02E06
description:
The Recruit - S02E06

Dedication is put to the test, as eight remain in the running for their dream prize: a contract with an AFL club. After a tough training session at the home of the Western Bulldogs, the recruits are shocked by an early morning wake-up from Barry Hall. All fly to Newcastle to compete in the Captain's Raw Challenge, and the winner runs the recruits out for a battle on the SCG against the Sydney Swans Academy. It's a strategic de-list but things don't go to everyone's plan and a favourite says goodbye.
